title: Eltone Mabodo
text: Applied micro (food security and nutrition) economist/data scientiest with 5+ years of experience in economic research and data science within academia, UN humanitarian projects, and policy think tanks. Skilled in Stata and R for quantitative analysis, with a strong focus on reproducible research using Git for collaboration. Master’s research on child nutrition in Zimbabwe published in an academic journal, driving evidence-based policy contributions.
